ns0:foreignObject.html:div: Look carefully at the image showing Elements of the weather. Use what you see to answer the following questions. Make sure to think about what you've learned in science class so far!

ns0:svg.ns0:text: 1. What are the main things you see in this picture related to the weather?
2. Can you point out and describe the different elements shown that help us understand the weather?
3. What does the image suggest about the current weather conditions?
4. How do the elements shown in the image affect our daily activities or decisions?
5. If you were to add one more element to the image to make it more informative, what would it be and why?
